<div class='row'>
  <div class='small-4 columns'>
    <div class='zoom-container'>
      <img src='/images/desert.jpg'>
      <div class='secret'><div class='text'>hello i am here</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='small-8 columns'>
    <h1>Clandestine Rendezvous</h1>
    <h4>You are a member of a secret society with a mission of the utmost importance.</h4>
    <h4>You will have encounters with other members around the PATH where you will obtain information to get closer to fulfilling your mission.</h4>
    <p>Clandestine Rendezvous is an adventure taking place in downtown Torontoâ€™s PATH <em>during the day</em> on Friday, February 5, 2016. Participants receive a set of appointment cards that direct them to specific locations at precise times at which they will meet other operatives and exchange information with them. Each rendezvous will provide a clue to solve the case.</p>

    <h2><i class='fa fa-question-circle'></i> Questions</h2>

    <%= form_for @conn, page_path(@conn, :questions), [as: :question], fn f -> %>
      <div class='form-group'>
        <%= label f, :name %>
        <%= text_input f, :name, class: "form-control" %>
      </div>

      <div class='form-group'>
        <%= label f, :email %>
        <%= text_input f, :email, class: "form-control" %>
      </div>

      <div class='form-group'>
        <%= label f, :subject %>
        <%= text_input f, :subject, class: "form-control" %>
      </div>

      <div class='form-group'>
        <%= label f, :question %>
        <%= textarea f, :question, class: "form-control" %>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <%= submit "Submit", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

  </div>
</div>
